  "identifier": "HB 84",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to legal liability for local governments and declaring an emergency.",
  "abstract": "Amend KRS 411.100, relating to a city's liability for damage done during the course of a riot, to provide that any form of local government shall be liable for damage done during the course of a riot if they could have prevented the damage.",
